title: 1-2-3 Skein Crochet
description: Requiring only three skeins of yarn or less, this collection provides a variety of designs that are fun and fast to finish. Using up remnants from previous projects or trying out samples of more expensive yarns, these designs are more flexible in order to make use of materials not feasible for larger projects.
